Model definition for Analytics.GoalUrlDestinationDetails. Details for the goal of the type URL_DESTINATION. This class models an object which will be transmitted to or from the Analytics service. To reduce the data transferred during service requests, you may remove members that contain data elements that your application does not need. For a detailed explanation, see: http://code.google.com/p/google-api-java-client/wiki/Json
